        <h2 class="title" style="text-align:center;"><a class="link-plain" href="/good-news">LOCAL GOOD (Powered by Do Some Good)</a></h2>

<p style="text-align:center;">What <span style="font-weight:700">GOOD</span> are you seeing in your community?</p>

<p style="text-align:center;"><span>Tell us about your favourite cause. Celebrate friends, family, and neighbours for their acts of kindness. Show your employees volunteering in the community. Ask for needed supplies and volunteers for your cause. Share fundraising event details.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<br>
Click <strong><a href="https://mailchi.mp/dosomegood/shareyourstories" target="_blank">HERE</a></strong> to find out how to get featured.&nbsp;</p>

